#: includes/ui_modal__shortcodes/sh_tpl_booking.php:1668
msgid ""
"For example, a visitor can choose to book 7 or 14 days or 21 days starting "
"on '2027-02-15'. To configure this, enter date in format 'YYYY-MM-DD' such "
"as '2027-02-15' and set the number of days to select as '7,14,21'. Click the "
"'Add Rule' button."
msgstr ""
"En besøgende kan f.eks. vælge at booke 7 eller 14 dage eller 21 dage fra "
"'2027-02-15'. For at konfigurere dette skal du indtaste dato i formatet "
